      <title>hexo常用命令</title>
      <link href="/posts/33f59116.html"/>
      <url>/posts/33f59116.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>清除缓存文件 (db.json) 和已生成的静态文件 (public)。<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>生成静态文件<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>部署网站，部署之前预先生成静态文件。<br><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
